		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I don't think speed would be a problem.
<br />
<br />What will be a problem is the capacitance and inductance.
<br />You could try to calculate it, and see if it will work.
<br />
<br />I say just try it, and see if it works. Use ribbon cable (like for IDE drives).

		

